				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/Bi%C3%AAn-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-glbctpgZsDML36OtywLITw">Biên cảnh - 邊警</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/author-1SPKfkHlUAnw6r-glqobvQ">Tạ Trăn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/C%C3%BAc-thu-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-L9avSEDvbXT_G3ZQAjLATA">Cúc thu bách vịnh kỳ 1 - 菊秋百詠其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Khi%C3%AAn/D%E1%BA%A1-h%C3%A0nh/poem-SioGNbRoiql5G9cwnhhMeg">Dạ hành - 夜行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Khi%C3%AAn/author-u7e1XRlJeAxu5ZlmUgP9_Q">Ngô Triệu Khiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99/poem-5yAkYyGVgv00bQlMfi_2Lg">Đề Tống Trân mộ - 題宋珍墓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Hi%E1%BB%83u-qu%C3%A1-Tr%E1%BA%A7m-H%C3%A0o-h%E1%BA%A3i-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-YWcAjPHITTX36xAiNgi-Bw">Hiểu quá Trầm Hào hải khẩu - 曉過沈濠海口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%91i-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BA%A7m-Th%C3%B4i-T%E1%BA%ADp-L%C3%BD-Phong/poem-neEex_nJbtbqxsomPgS_KA">Hối nhật tầm Thôi Tập, Lý Phong - 晦日尋崔戢李封</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-D%C6%B0-Ngh%C4%A9a/L%C3%A2m-giang-ti%C3%AAn-D%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C4%83ng-ti%E1%BB%83u-c%C3%A1c-%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BB%B1u-du/poem-ItUoIH1-LIgTsNsAgRogFQ">Lâm giang tiên - Dạ đăng tiểu các ức cựu du - 臨江仙－夜登小閣憶舊遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-D%C6%B0-Ngh%C4%A9a/author-_2_KNqIhiUMk8s_AJgW7Nw">Trần Dư Nghĩa</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-D%E1%BB%AF/Ngh%C4%A9-T%E1%BB%AB-Th%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-ti%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%AD-Gi%C3%A1ng-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%9F-c%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%91-b%C3%ACnh-phong-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-fQ-G2hEaF-aAtvMS2nzuiw">Nghĩ Từ Thức đề tiên tử Giáng Hương sở cư tố bình phong kỳ 1 - 擬徐式題仙子絳香所居素屏風其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-D%E1%BB%AF/author-7mP7WEruGTN9xvlXIibdrw">Nguyễn Dữ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/Tri%E1%BB%81u-h%E1%BB%93i-h%E1%BB%89-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mIFtbpooOMqE0Nxb_Ltxw">Triều hồi hỉ phú - 朝回喜賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-Ptt2M8z98OAIiQfyBrIxHw">Vũ Huy Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Gi%E1%BA%A3i/V%C3%A3n-ph%C3%A1t-Quan-San/poem-bG-DdaqlDLhxBlhhu2FvFQ">Vãn phát Quan San - 晚發關山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Gi%E1%BA%A3i/author-try44H72AY-hBcH61r-NIQ">Trịnh Giải</a>)<br></div>	</div>
